      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver at a reasonable price. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable signs of its age, including some minor exterior scratches, interior upholstery wear, and a few small mechanical items that will likely need attention in the near future. It has been used regularly and maintained to a basic standard, ensuring it stays on the road, though it lacks the polish of a newer or better-kept model. This is an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
