      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The drivetrain is anchored by a functional M-Variable differential lock, providing exceptional power delivery through the rear wheels. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a structural subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. Equipped with an OEM-spec suspension that maintains factory-level damping and rebound characteristics, this vehicle offers the precise turn-in and mechanical feedback expected of the M-division's peak engineering.",
