      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a prime example of a well-loved executive sedan, balancing performance with everyday utility. Finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic, the exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of careful highway use\u2014the body remains straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the Cognac Dakota leather interior has been meticulously preserved; the bolsters show minimal wear, and the cabin remains a strict non-smoker environment. All technology features, including the gesture control and Harman Kardon surround sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It has been serviced exclusively at certified centers, with a recent brake fluid flush and a fresh set of Continental all-season tires installed last season. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six runs smoothly, providing effortless power without any hesitations. This car offers a refined driving experience for the buyer who appreciates a vehicle that has been maintained with an eye for detail.",
